column5: Big Fatty is a black chicken. She has brown legs and holds the record for being the heaviest chicken. She even beats Cookie and the Black Jersey GIANTS!!!
column6: She likes to right there when Daddy is digging in the pen
column7: She is really high in the pecking order, and therefore gets most everything she wants

column5: BP is a black chicken with with orangish-gold on her breast. She was given away because of her name. She was indeed a Black Pecky.
column6: she loves Anton, but came up to Sofia when Sofia entered the pen just to peck Sofia.
column7: she is a very good layer.

column5: Cookie III is an Aracauna Rooster, he is very colorful and wonderful.
